children.subject: Yes you can always audit the course! The app comes out around the beginning of the semester. Look out for a banner on our website and a post on our facebook page when the application is released around the beginning of the semester.
Hi! May I know when the app to be a student will come out? And will there be an option to audit the class?

history.content:
<md>The Web Design DeCal will be offered for Spring 2021, and we're looking for TAs to join the team! If you have any web design and development experience, we encourage you to apply at https://forms.gle/MkVZScdPRokP4wcf8 by **this Sunday, January 10**. You do not need to have taken the decal before, and you can check out more details of our decal on our website, http://wdd.io/.

Class will be held over Zoom on Tuesdays 7-8:30pm PST and Thursdays 7-8pm PST. TA responsibilities include attending staff meetings on Thursdays at 6:30-7pm before class, answering questions during class, hosting office hours, and updating curriculum. Being a TA for WDD is extremely rewarding, and you can also receive two PNP units. 

If you have any questions about the course or the TA app, feel free to post a follow-up!</md>
